      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a new home. It's in really nice shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that won't break the bank, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
