    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 features the high-revving F22C1 inline-four, delivering linear power delivery and an 8,000 RPM redline. The longitudinal drivetrain is anchored by a precise six-speed short-throw manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution through the corners. Its rigid X-bone frame and four-wheel double-wishbone suspension provide exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Recently serviced with a focus on valve clearances and fluid integrity, this chassis remains a benchmark for naturally aspirated performance and mechanical balance.",
