      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior shines with a deep gloss, showing only minor road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, while the cabin's technology suite functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound, having received consistent scheduled servicing; the engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. Recent additions include a fresh set of all-season tires and a complete brake service. It is a smoke-free, pet-free environment that smells as clean as it looks. Whether you're commuting or embarking on a weekend getaway, this car offers a refined experience that belies its age and is ready for its next owner.",
